## Database Constraints

### Check Constraints

```ruby
# Ensure value meets condition
add_check_constraint :articles, 
                     "length(title) >= 5",
                     name: "title_min_length"

add_check_constraint :products,
                     "price > 0",
                     name: "price_positive"
```

### Exclusion Constraints (PostgreSQL)

```ruby
# Prevent overlapping values
execute <<-SQL
  ALTER TABLE bookings
  ADD CONSTRAINT no_overlapping_bookings
  EXCLUDE USING gist (room_id WITH =, daterange(start_date, end_date) WITH &&)
SQL
```

